Prebon/Ignatius

Prebon gave Spears one last kiss before Ignatius was swept into the 
air.

"Remember, your best performance ever."

Ignatius went into the air as everyone started moving. Ignatius spoke 
with Spears.

"So what's with you and the boss? Yoy've hardly been here a day and 
he's all over you. Blaze has been trying for years and not a single 
thing has happened."
